{"tid":2205930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國駐聯合國大使：美國願為台灣香港挺身對抗中國","createTime":"2020-09-17T06:59:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T20:05:56.000Z","uid":337052,"like":455,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"79afca245153349caa26fe338f36a2ba45bd0c6d","tid":2205930,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:59:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">【美高調挺台】重大突破！美駐聯合國大使首晤我駐紐約代表 承諾「助台參與聯合國事務」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/YW4JlWk7tJQpuVQ1UrLgsteNgDk=/760x506/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2AN3IF2MEBDJZOADYMDGTRMJ2I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYW4JlWk7tJQpuVQ1UrLgsteNgDk%3D%2F760x506%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2AN3IF2MEBDJZOADYMDGTRMJ2I.jpg&h=f1b0a3f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美駐聯合國大使克拉夫特與駐紐約台北經濟文化辦事處李光章，16日在紐約曼哈頓一間戶外餐廳共進午餐，並由美聯社記者側拍。 美聯社<br />\n在美國國務次卿克拉奇（Keith Krach）即將到訪台灣之際，美國駐聯合國大使克拉夫特（Kelly Craft）周三（16日）也與台灣駐紐約的最高官員、駐紐約台北經濟文化辦事處李光章共進午餐。克拉夫特表示，這次會晤具「歷史性」意義，也代表川普政府更進一步強化與台灣關係。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">克拉夫特向美聯社表示，她和李光章在紐約上東城一間戶外餐廳共進午餐，也是台灣駐紐約最高級官員首度與美國駐聯合國大使用餐。她向李光章承諾，將協助台灣參與聯合國事務。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">克拉夫特說，台灣應該要能夠像所有其他國家一樣參與聯合國事務，「如果美國不為台灣挺身對抗中國，那麼誰會挺身而出？不只台灣，還有香港，還有其他地方？」</span><br />\n<br />\n報導指出，李光章原為外交部主任秘書，才剛赴紐約上任。他邀請克拉夫特共進午餐，克拉夫特欣然受邀。克拉夫特說，「這是東道國歡迎他很好的方式，聽他談談他的家庭、他的經歷」，「以及台灣能提供世界的&hellip;&hellip;許多許多創新科技」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/MHyV5QG751d4QOrcyC85jyMFxC0=/760x506/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q3QPQYZIASGXQPB3KXHPL64SOM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMHyV5QG751d4QOrcyC85jyMFxC0%3D%2F760x506%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ3QPQYZIASGXQPB3KXHPL64SOM.gif&h=2d1c3532&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美駐聯合國大使克拉夫特與駐紐約台北經濟文化辦事處李光章，周三在曼哈頓一間戶外餐廳共進午餐，是美駐聯合國大使首度與台灣駐紐約最高官員會晤。 美聯社<br />\n<br />\n克拉夫特表示，她想跟隨總統做正確的事，「我認為他想強化且深化與台灣的雙邊關係，我想代表政府延續這樣的作為」<br />\n<br />\n克拉夫特與李光章會晤的翌日，就是國務次卿克拉奇抵達台灣訪問之日，勢將使美中關係更加緊張。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社分析，美國與民主台灣的關係近來升溫，受到國會兩黨強烈支持，也顯示川普政府有意違抗北京威脅，宣揚不同於中共極權主義的政體。<br />\n<br />\n分析指，川普政府積極促使讓台灣以獨立實體的方式加入世界組織，如世界衛生組織（WHO）和世界民航組織（ICAO），也極力遏阻北京對台的外交勝利。 （國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/NhGQ6oG3KSckAeQNs9goEKZLLHI=/760x506/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2LL4J5KX5RH2VH7Z33KI4LBZCU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNhGQ6oG3KSckAeQNs9goEKZLLHI%3D%2F760x506%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2LL4J5KX5RH2VH7Z33KI4LBZCU.jpg&h=9b4025f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n克拉夫特原為美國駐加拿大大使，去年9月成為駐聯合國大使。 資料照片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/5oUCtNi-NKyx4vztM4HRJP5shZQ=/4765x3177/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/II3SI7Q6DNFWLHKIT5A5DNFWQ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5oUCtNi-NKyx4vztM4HRJP5shZQ%3D%2F4765x3177%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FII3SI7Q6DNFWLHKIT5A5DNFWQ4.jpg&h=6e087b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美駐聯合國大使克拉夫特與駐紐約台北經濟文化辦事處李光章，周三在曼哈頓一間戶外餐廳共進午餐。 美聯社<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200917/VHQV27IBAREOJNFTUMF4C5K5KY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200917%2FVHQV27IBAREOJNFTUMF4C5K5KY%2F&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2Bo26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=7c743df3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200917%2FVHQV27IBAREOJNFTUMF4C5K5KY%2F&h=20a4e26e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200917/VHQV27IBAREOJNFTUMF4C5K5KY/</a>"},{"pid":"ff9ca64dac931f471015d94575bedcb04c529a1e","tid":2205930,"uid":337052,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T07:02:45.000Z","msg":"克拉夫特說，台灣應該要能夠像所有其他國家一樣參與聯合國事務，「如果美國不為台灣挺身對抗中國，那麼誰會挺身而出？不只台灣，還有香港，還有其他地方？」"},{"pid":"a027a40daa9024991e6ec88485f058745cb036f0","tid":2205930,"uid":41116,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T07:03:35.000Z","msg":"they can talk the talk<br />\nbut can they walk the walk?"},{"pid":"fcf363f39e74c249fa1fe9eb109b9ee6f828144f","tid":2205930,"uid":160963,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T07:03:43.000Z","msg":"快d派美軍解放香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466bd9fadf6fb355db42be01b8d41293feac56fc","tid":2205930,"uid":135408,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T07:03:45.000Z","msg":"到底美國想唔想繼續玩聯合國嫁"},{"pid":"7e6624f90806589e9b019174e87e812a2f46d189","tid":2205930,"uid":146030,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T07:04:36.000Z","msg":"香港獨立之後整條trump road"},{"pid":"58e4e1db7e5fc5686efd57b03af694724aad30ee","tid":2205930,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T07:05:02.000Z","msg":"US envoy to United Nations meets with Taiwan official in NY<br />\n<a href=\"https://mooresvilletribune.com/news/national/us-envoy-to-united-nations-meets-with-taiwan-official-in-ny/article_0d920376-5a6d-5f23-b9ad-791558d88580.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmooresvilletribune.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fus-envoy-to-united-nations-meets-with-taiwan-official-in-ny%2Farticle_0d920376-5a6d-5f23-b9ad-791558d88580.html&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2Bo26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=ab428944\" target=\"_